{
  "stem": "18575.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 370.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Polish Army, of course, was no match for Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was mostly cavalry with swords attacking tanks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Germans had fun sitting on a tank and machine-gunning them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it held out for about a week, till there was no more water, there was no more electricity, there was no more food, and then capitulated.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We used to sit the kids-- sit on the roofs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The roofs on Warsaw buildings were metal roofs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some were slated-- not flat roof-- not very steep, but some were slated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We used to sit on a roof, and when the Germans bombed with the incendiary bombs, the phosphor bombs, they would fall.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were canisters.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it would takes about 20, 30 seconds before they start exploding, and they would shoot out phosphor, which would go right through the metal roof and start the fires.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The thing was that if it fell on  a roof, to throw it off into the garden, to push it off to the garden.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Luckily, our house was never bombed, so we just sat and watched them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I actually could see the pilots when they would dive bombing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You could-- that how close they used to come in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we used to lay on the roof and watch them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But there were kids and the other roof also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so that was our playground, you know, sitting on the roof.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was exciting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't-- not that I recall.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't know if they-- they knew what I was doing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, we ran out of food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a-- a small contingent of Polish cavalry stationed in the garden of our house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somehow or other, I don't know by what means, but a couple of the horses got killed.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
